{
  "stem": "268.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I spoke good Polish and without a, a Yiddish accent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I-- and I would sing songs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he liked one particular song about, about five sailors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he told me later a story that he was a merchant sailor before the war, a merchant marine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he'd say, sing that song!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And, you know, he, he would have separate quarters for himself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he had an orderly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he had plenty of food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And of course, he-- I, I would get extra soup, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And that, that saved my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Except I-- for what is-- you know, I, I, I disliked the guy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But I had to sing for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But after he-- after he-- I saw him-- actually-- and, and I know he was a killer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He would-- you know, he would beat up-- [? but, but I-- ?] but after, after one-- if, if I may, I'd like to tell a story about-- one time he told me, he says, you know, you don't have to go to outside work.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You can-- you can work in a barrack if you want to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I says-- cleaning.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I said, that's fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So he gave me a good job cleaning up the barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he says, and then in the evening, when the soup comes, you're in charge.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You, you distribute the soup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He gave me a ladle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And he says-- and he showed me how to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "He says, don't pay attention to those creatures-- those, those creeps-- the creeps-- the Muselmann.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Don't pay attention to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They'll always say, stir it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Stir it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Don't pay attention to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Just take-- they line up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And he says, give everybody-- and he showed me that ladle-- don't ever get-- run over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "He says, up to the rim.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
